  "2026-06-26T19:05:47.336Z",codex-codefactor-sdk-cli-20260626,"Evidence: CodeFactor complexity scope now ignores generated standalone loaders, generated standalone launchers, and tests while keeping shipped source files in analysis; create/update unset parsing tables were collapsed into shared metadata to reduce command surface duplication and maintenance cost. Manual temp smoke in /tmp/tmp.XalxjTQCOu passed init, create, update --unset deadline/assignee, package install todos --project, package doctor --project --detail deep, contracts --flags-only, and health --check-only --summary with only telemetry_queue_pending local warning."
  "2026-06-26T20:02:53.988Z",codex,"CodeFactor complexity follow-up: current safe branch removed duplication and verified strict local duplicate_chunks=[] at max-complexity=100. The remaining strict-local complexity rows are broad command handlers/register surfaces: registerMutationCommands complexity 251, runUpdate 222, mcp runAction 188, runCreate 173, update mutate 145, runExtension 142, runConfig 124, plus three test closures over 100. These are not closed by this duplication-focused PR; pm-arzz remains open for staged complexity refactors so command behavior is not destabilized by an oversized rewrite."
